			            <div class="rt-block-ident-1">
			              <h2 class="ident-bot-5">Union Tool Makes 
			                Automated Machines... </h2>
			              <h3>...that handle and process flat sheets, boards and panels made of wood, metal, glass,   plastic, fiber or foam.</h3>
			              <p>&nbsp;</p>
			              <p>&nbsp;</p>
			              <div class="ident-bot-6">
			                <p>Roller coaters, automated press feeders, stackers, hot melt applicators, laminators, lubricators, turn-over devices... whatever can be done with sheets, panels and boards in a conveyorized processing line, Union Tool makes the automated machines and equipment that do it.</p>
		                  </div>
			              <p><a class="button" href="union_tool_machines.html">learn more</a></p>
